data.title: Expensive but tastes delicious and does the body well
data.text:
I wish there were more cold pressed juicing places around everywhere so that the competition made the prices lower. This place makes an amazing detox smoothie (I ordered the biggest size) and purchased a bottled juice to go (also a green juice). Cost me around $16 for 2 drinks. You can drink deliciously healthy but it'll definitely cost you so it's only something I get as a treat or while away on vacation and have no access to a blender. 
However, I really enjoyed the juice and the friendly staff and will continue to go in the future. Parking in this lot is atrocious by the way. Expect a 10 minute delay in finding parking anywhere around 11am to 2pm.
